The Surfr. App is a performance tracking app for Kite boarders. With the app kite boarders can record, view and share their performance:
- Jumps (height, airtime, distance)

Also the app is able to track the path the user has surfed over water. This path/track can optionally be stored as well.

The Surfr. App is meant to be used with a board mount in order to mount a phone to a kite board.
